{"tid":1562113,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曝普巴與巴黎談成50萬週薪協議 尼馬連帶告吹","createTime":"2019-09-12T01:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T08:44:01.000Z","uid":59732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25781ab98d8187d95f352abc4516d6c2832438f5","tid":1562113,"uid":59732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/09/12/d/db54d2cdf81404f46ae88e8a591c2cdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2Fd%2Fdb54d2cdf81404f46ae88e8a591c2cdc.jpg&h=67b9cafd&s={SIZE}\" />據意大利媒體披露，在轉會截止日前，曼聯球星普巴與巴黎聖日耳門私下談妥了一份週薪50萬歐元的合約，但因為尼馬的交易失敗，普巴的這一轉會也沒能成功。<br />\n<br />\n　　意大利《Calciomercato》稱，在轉會關窗之前，曼聯和巴黎聖日耳門達成了轉會協議，同意將普巴賣給聖日耳曼，法國人和巴黎還達成了個人合約協議，週薪高達50萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n　　不過，由於巴黎沒能賣掉尼馬，普巴的這一交易也受到了影響，最終未能成功。<br />\n<br />\n　　另有消息稱，贊助商Adidas在阻止普巴離開曼聯時也起了作用，他們不希望看到法國人離開自己贊助的紅魔。<br />\n<br />\n　　不過，普巴本人在曼聯並不安分，除了夏天公開表態希望轉會，他的哥哥近日還透露，普巴聯絡了美斯、基沙文、華拉尼等人，詢問西甲的一些情況。看起來，夏天時留在曼聯對普巴來說似乎只是權宜之計，如果紅魔的成績沒有起色，普巴想走的意願不會改變。"},{"pid":"d56c6e32baf2e7e1d034121c72c34534a24fc0ad","tid":1562113,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:34:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"65e011